# API Configuration
# 
# For development with real device, you have 3 options:
#
# Option 1: Use your computer's local IP (recommended)
# Find your IP: ipconfig getifaddr en0 (Mac) or ipconfig (Windows)
# Example: API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8000/api
#
# Option 2: Use localhost (only works on emulator)
# API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
#
# Option 3: Use ngrok tunnel (works anywhere)
# Start ngrok: ngrok http 8000
# Example: API_BASE_URL=https://abc123.ngrok.io/api
#
# For production:
# API_BASE_URL=https://api-portfolio.instocks.net/api

# CHANGE THIS TO YOUR ACTUAL SETUP:
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
